                "title": "<p>23. How to use the <strong>Nostril retainer</strong> (nostril shaper apparatus)?</p>",
                "text": "<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">The purpose of the nostril retainer product is not to give a shape to the nose, but to ensure that the nose shape created in the surgery heals symmetrically.</span></p><p>Sometimes you need to start using it during surgery and sometimes when the tampons inside the nose come out.</p><p><br></p><p>It is used to reduce risks such as possible asymmetry, nasal tip shape problems by healing on this mold during the nasal healing process.</p><p><br></p><blockquote>Usage method:</blockquote><blockquote>My routine recommendation is to use it <strong>24 hours a day for 2 months, and then 8-12 hours a day for 2 months </strong>from the moment you start using it.</blockquote><blockquote>Since usage time and details may vary from patient to patient, the process specific to you will be explained to you in control evaluations.</blockquote>"
